# Navigation Bar Guidelines

## § 3.3 Navigation Bar

- Horizontal bar fixed to top of page, full width
- Does not appear on landing page or `Home.svelte`
- Only appears on `ParseMode.svelte` and `FlashcardMode.svelte`

## § 1.0 States

### Collapsed (Default)
- Only shows icons
- Icons centered on navigation bar

### Expanded
- When `Open.svelte` is clicked, reveals text labels
- Text appears to the right of each icon
- Icons shift to accommodate text
- Icons and text remain centered

## § 2.0 Icon Order (Left to Right)

1. `Open.svelte` / `Collapse.svelte` — Dashboard toggle (far left)
2. `SentenceLibrary.svelte` — "Sentences"
3. `DeckLibrary.svelte` — "Decks"
4. `Settings.svelte` — "Settings"
5. `HowToUse.svelte` — "How To Use"
6. `Login.svelte` — "Login" (far right)

